
  <sn><md>### To vs Toward

&gt; To - Destination <br>
&gt; Toward - Direction

**Example**

- They are going `to` the station. (`destination`)
- They are going `toward` the station. (`direction`)

**Problem**

- I am going `toward` the station to receive my parents. ❌
- I am going `to` the station to receive my parents. ✅
